txt.en: 'The farmhouses are rebuilt, the crops are planted, and it is time to put forth the call for farmers to come and join Hytbold. With them, we will truly be self-sufficient and able to stand upon our own two feet. Maybe soon, we will have enough food that we can send aid to the others who are in need.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
